reviewText: These are VHS tapes, hard to find today. My friend has a VHS player and has used them in the past. She loves the tapes, and is happy.
They're in good condition. Add these 4 Tae Bo Live tapes in your Tae Bo video library.

I chose this rating because it's not a another boring silly work out. You can feel the burn the whole time and know what part of your body you'reis working.
I would recommend this work out for anyone who is trying to tone up or lose weight.
My sister and I had these tapes when they first came out years ago I and we wore them out.  I lost 40lbs using these then. So excited I found them again because have tried other work out tapes that have nothing on this -number ready to tone up now!!!
